        "setup": "In Bob, open the Service Users configuration page and create a new service user, then copy its ID and token. If you do not have direct access, ask a Bob admin to generate it for you. After creating it, assign the service user to a dedicated permission group as described in [API Service users](https://apidocs.hibob.com/docs/api-service-users) and [Manage service users](https://help.hibob.com/hc/en-us/articles/27875098648465-Manage-service-users). Use the pair as HTTP Basic auth by base64-encoding ``SERVICE-USER-ID:TOKEN`` into the `Authorization` header."
